com.madrobot.net.client.async

Class AsyncHttpRequestParams

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.madrobot.net.client.async.AsyncHttpRequestParams

  • public class AsyncHttpRequestParams
extends Object
    A collection of string request parameters or files to send along with requests made from an AsyncHttpClient instance.

    For example: 

     RequestParams params = new RequestParams();
 params.put("username", "james");
 params.put("password", "123456");
 params.put("email", "my@email.com");
 params.put("profile_picture", new File("pic.jpg")); // Upload a File
 params.put("profile_picture2", someInputStream); // Upload an InputStream
 params.put("profile_picture3", new ByteArrayInputStream(someBytes)); // Upload
                                                                                                                                                // some
                                                                                                                                                // bytes
 
 AsyncHttpClient client = new AsyncHttpClient();
 client.post("http://myendpoint.com", params, responseHandler);
